How to make Cinematic Frame using Vn Editor. 

Steps to follow
1. Open Vn and Import Video
2. Click on pip timeline and choose black image from stock
3. Click on fill, it will cover the whole area
4. Than click on mask option and chose rectangle frame and double click on it
5. Adjust frame according to your video
6. Than click and stretch the top left arrow to make the frame look cinematic

Janagana Mana, A Review -

From the death of professor in University of Hyderabad thhat ignited discussions about the cheap casteism floating in Indiaâs educational institutions to r@pe cases.. to the recent encounter killings of accused rapists in Hyderabad... the film has touched upon many relevant political contents...

Jana Gana Mana is a politically favoured film purposefully designed to evoke a gut reaction from its viewer and is a film that tries to start a deliberation of societal stigma revolving around religious, class, caste identities.... The director is clear with the form of resistance well disguised in the package of a fast paced, intriguing, commercial entertainer.

The lack of unnecessary songs disrupting the flow of the story adds to the effect of the film. Speaking of music the music director gives the support the screenplay needs to leave the audience at the edge of their seats...
For those expecting a faceoff between Prithviraj and Suraj after their wonderful performances in Driving License this might come as a disappointment....

Worth a watch...
